<db:synopsisinfo role="status">active</db:synopsisinfo>
<db:synopsisinfo role="threadsafeness">unspecified</db:synopsisinfo>
</db:methodsynopsis>
<db:para>This is a convenience function that can be used directly instead of resolving the function pointer. Returns true if Windows 10 operates in <db:emphasis>Tablet Mode</db:emphasis>. In this mode, Windows forces all application main windows to open in maximized state. Applications should then avoid resizing windows or restoring geometries to non-maximized states.</db:para>
<db:para>This function was introduced in Qt 5.9.</db:para>
